  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The silver eyed witches, a mix between demons and humans are the only ones who can fight against the demons that ravages the land.With the sword Claymore in hand, release the demonic powers in your blood, but stop before this power corrupts the you. An over-dependence on it may turn you into the monster that you are fighting.\n\nThe game system is easy to master, with a few taps on the touch screen panel, you can unleash the powers in your blood and launch sure kill attacks.Besides Claire, the heroine, you can to take control of other characters and test out their skills and limits. Sink deeper into the dark, dangerous world of Claymore no longer as a spectator, but as a warrior.",
